This is the protocol for a review and there is no abstract. The objectives are as follows:, To compare intravitreal low molecular weight heparin alone or with 5-Fluorouracil to placebo as an adjunct in the prevention of proliferative vitreoretinopathy following retinal reattachment surgery., The null hypothesis is that there is no difference between intravitreal low molecular weight heparin and placebo as an adjunct for the prevention of proliferative vitreoretinopathy following retinal reattachment surgery